{
  "stem": "23428.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, you know, from hindsight, I know now that actually the crematoria were blown up at that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that practice did-- was stopped because the Red Army, in fact, had-- had approached very close.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, maybe before I tell you about the march to Auschwitz-- one, I should tell you, that in the-- in the few days before that, I was drafted into a work detail that shipped furniture and personal belongings of SS people from their villas onto trains.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- we carried out the-- we were movers-- we were employed as movers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one of the fortunate things that happened in that transaction, in that work detail, is that one of the SS officers threw me a pair of old boots that I wore for months afterwards.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they get a piece of luck, you see, because once your feet are frozen off, that was extremely important to have-- to have shoes that-- that would not leak-- the snow would not leak through.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I had these good boots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, again, you know, why the hell he took pity on me, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I suspect seeing an innocent 17-year-old who obviously had nothing to do with all of this-- couldn't even comprehend any of it-- he must have seen that somehow.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not at all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, not at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was absolutely zero information.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And also no concern, you see, because once you've given up on your life, you-- you don't worry about anymore what goes on outside.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was actually no political-- even the political interest or discussion or anything like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody kept pretty much to-- for himself, largely-- as I mentioned already-- for fear of being turned in, if you said the wrong thing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
